snippet.title: Time Donkey Trailer
snippet.description:
Follow the adventures of the Donkey, inadvertently trapped in the same 30 seconds of time, over and over again. What will he do? Can he escape? And why are there tacos everywhere?

Time Donkey is our 9th game, available to play free on Blurst.com.
